            "text" : "**Seeking a Stronger Punchline**\n\nI'm working to refine the humor request. The prior attempt, the \"atoms\" joke, wasn't quite landing. I'm aiming for something with a more intricate structure, perhaps a clever setup or a narrative twist, to increase the impact of the punchline. Currently, I'm exploring an animal-based joke structure, using a horse.\n\n\n",
